title: Current Prices Received; Percent of Respondents Reporting Decreases for Federal Reserve District 3: Philadelphia
notes: Current Prices Received reports the change in prices received compared to the previous month for reporting service firms. For more information about this release from the Federal Reserve Bank of Philadelphia, visit: http://www.philadelphiafed.org/research-and-data/regional-economy/nonmanufacturing-business-outlook-survey/ .
